0060#STR0060#ALL#Enter from which PCMSO it must be displayed in the report. Press [F3]+[Enter] to select an PCMSO.
0061#STR0061#ALL#Enter until which PCMSO it must be displayed in the report. Press [F3]+[Enter] to select the desired PCMSO or type ZZZZZZ in this field and leave the one above in blank to consider all PCMSO.
0062#STR0062#ALL#Enter from which Test it must be displayed in the report. Press [F3]+[Enter] to select an Test.
