0065#STR0065#ALL#Enter until which Sched. Date must be displayed in the report. Press [F3]+[Enter] to select a Sched. Date or type ZZZZZZ in this field and leave the field above blank to consider all Models.
0066#STR0066#ALL#Enter from which Cost Center it must be displayed in the report. Press [F3]+[Enter] to select a Cost Center.
0067#STR0067#ALL#Enter until which Cost Center it must be displayed in the report. Press [F3]+[Enter] to select the desired Cost Center or type ZZZZZZ in this field and leave the one above in blank to consider all Assets.
